mbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9iUsZ4.png&h=657a767b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>網民自發遊行光復屯門公園<br />\n《東張西望》遭指罵出賣港人<br />\n<br />\n【即時】(14:45) 網民及屯門衛生關注組下午自發到屯門公園進行光復行動，不滿公園十多年來被噪音問題滋擾，斥責更有大媽行乞和賣淫。<br />\n<br />\n多間媒體到場採訪，無綫電視節目《東張西望》主持林泳淘欲訪問參與行動的示威者時，遭示威者指罵，稱不應接受出賣香港人的電影台訪問，「滾回大灣區」。<br />\n<br />\n林泳淘反駁稱，「我不是無綫新聞，係東張西望，我哋都係香港人嚟。」但在示威者群情洶湧下，《東張西望》的攝影團隊離開集會的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=cc50224e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=72383a1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://inmediahk.net/donate</a></blockquote><br />\nWingto不開心 但Wingto不說"},{"pid":"cd4ee0bfec6ffca72eee14705e293949ed75135b","tid":1289541,"uid":79562,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"a0601c89db72fc2f0d2e7201211f45170c2584bf","tid":1289541,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:58:01.000Z","msg":"咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:03:54.000Z","msg":"探訪比人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明公開反送中比人雪咗一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb0c50d9e1d9ab58d31771c3cd6f52815c6e7ee","tid":1289541,"uid":251052,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"要鬧就鬧袁志偉 唔關wingto事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d986beba389021a044323c9df024d0dc3b55411f","tid":1289541,"uid":19552,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"東張狙擊班大媽勇