聞，係東張西望，我哋都係香港人嚟。」但在示威者群情洶湧下，《東張西望》的攝影團隊離開集會的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=cc50224e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=72383a1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://inmediahk.net/donate</a></blockquote><br />\nWingto不開心 但Wingto不說"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"咁撚醒目揾女神黎挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本部份cctvb女神都係班主管打造"},{"pid":"f463e57f695be72309645b21e57cf70e93880d46","tid":1289541,"uid":13033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"351683f2e2cb27d218caa928f86c85cca4482ee2","tid":1289541,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d986beba389021a044323c9df024d0dc3b55411f","tid":1289541,"uid":19552,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"東張狙擊班大媽勇武左好多次 真係唔應該反"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"呢樣真"},{"pid":"722d8059920f7ffed57f450fe70e8e39dff652b4","tid":1289541,"uid":74278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"大佬冇睇tvb鬼知佢邊個<br />\n淨係知佢tvb<br />\n同埋點解憎東張西望就叫佢問下吳幸美啦"},{"pid":"65f0d388b8aed5a9ffb2cd60d261ff5c5b757a44","tid":1289541,"uid":115245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"其實東張西望成日狙擊呢D野.....屌乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c101c7c438f395881ebfd47b4d2501e7688f83","tid